    <title>安装butterfly主题</title>
    <link href="https://hfghfgdshf.github.io/posts/53943.html"/>
    <id>https://hfghfgdshf.github.io/posts/53943.html</id>
    <published>2025-08-24T11:23:54.000Z</published>
    <updated>2025-08-24T12:54:08.868Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>1、安装butterfly</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git clone -b master https://github.com/jerryc127/hexo-theme-butterfly.git themes/butterfly</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>下载完之后根目录下会出现一个theme文件夹，里面就是主题文件</p><p>2、应用主题</p><p>a、将根目录文件夹下的_config.yml文件中的主题应用改为butterfly</p><p>b、安装渲染器</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-renderer-pug hexo-renderer-stylus --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>c、在根目录创建一个_config.butterfly.yml文件，将主题文件中_config.yml文件内容复制到_config,butterfly.yml文件中</p><p>后期配置主题插件时一般只需更改_config.butterfly.yml文件，并且其优先级更高</p><p>注意：</p><p>前面安装butterfly使用的是GitHub如果下载失败可能需要科学上网，或者使用gitee下载：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git clone -b master https://gitee.com/immyw/hexo-theme-butterfly.git themes/butterfly</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>下载完成后依次输入：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo cl</span><br><span class="line">hexo g</span><br><span class="line">hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>最后会生成一个网站，打开即可本地查看效果</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
